!!++
!! SURF_ZERNIKE01.INR
!! Title: ZERNIKE Surface
!! Category: Isolated Command
!! Keywords: ZERNIKE, SURFACE
!! Description: A simple zernike surface using
!! four coefficients.
!! Edit History: (latest first)
!! 02/28/2002 - cp - corrected style
!! 10/16/2000 - cp - modified format; added description
!! 01/01/1996 - bro - creation
!!--

SYSTEM NEW
RESET

SURFACE
  ZERNIKE Z 0  0 0 0 .5
OBJECT
  
WINDOW Y Z  !! To view object
WINDOW 1.5
PLOT FACETS 5 5 'SURF:ZERNIKE' COLORS 11
RETURN